The paper proposes a novel approach to robot system design that integrates algorithmic planning and deep learning. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Robotics (cs.RO), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), and Systems and Control (cs.SY). However, given that the paper focuses on a specific application of the proposed approach to a challenging partially observable robot navigation task, it is most likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The other sub-categories are also likely given the use of deep learning and recurrent neural networks, as well as the reliance on visual observations from an onboard camera.
